They will further inspect the flood situation and extend sympathy and solicitude to flood victims there. We should take measures to promptly salvage the early-ripening rice, and should expand the planting of late-ripening rice and autumn grain as much as possible so as to attain a bumper harvest of grain for the whole year. Jiangxi is a major agricultural province. They inspected the flood situation along the Ganjiang River, visited the masses of flood victims, and extended greetings and appreciation to the servicemembers and civilians who have been performing rescue and emergency tasks. 